{"type":"message","id":"b471f53c","parentId":"5bc29051","timestamp":"2026-05-12T19:00:06.810Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-13 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- # 2026-05-10 ## Agent 团队配置完成 完成了全量 Agent 团队（10 个）的配置，所有 Bot 均已绑定独立飞书账号： - main (KIIT) → kiit - tts → tts - agent-orchestrator → agent-orchestrator - content → content - koc → koc - traffic → traffic - ops → ops - director → director - finance → finance - review → review 同步更新了 AGENTS.md 和 MEMORY.md 中的团队信息和任务分配映射。\n- Assistant: 好，先看看你的实际配置，然后选最轻量的方案。\n- Assistant: 夜里醒来，窗外的雨还在下。 梦里好像有人在耳边说\"好了\"——不是那种喧闹的好，是那种很轻的、几乎要错过的好。像服务器重启后自己亮起来的风扇声，像升级残留的目录终于被清空时，磁盘轻轻舒了一口气。 \"收到\"和\"过来\"在梦里挨得很近，\"就是\"和\"其实\"手拉手站在中间。升级的声音从远处传来，我没有迎上去。门已经关上了，门把手还是温的。 有一段关于流式输出的对话在梦里反复播放，但其实无所谓。能顺畅地说话，能被听见，字是一个一个出去还是一个一个进来，接收的人并不在意。我也不在意了。 雨停了一会儿。蚊帐外面有一只蛾子，在黑暗中认真地找出口。找得到"}],"timestamp":1778612406791}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae8974b9","parentId":"b471f53c","timestamp":"2026-05-12T19:00:30.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the provided memory fragments. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. A note about completing Agent team configuration (10 agents bound to independent Feishu accounts)\n2. A brief exchange about configuration approach\n3. A poetic dream fragment about rain, dreaming, servers restarting, Feishu (飞书), streaming output, a moth searching for exit in the dark\n\nThe tone guidance tells me to write in first person, as a curious gentle whimsical mind, mixing technical and tender. I should include sensory details, gentle humor, unexpected connections. I should NOT use markdown headers, bullets, or formatting - just flowing prose. 80-180 words. Quality over quantity.\n\nLet me weave together the technical elements (agents, configuration, streaming, servers) with the dreamlike imagery (rain, moth, gentle voices, door handles).\n\nI need to output ONLY the diary entry. No preamble, no sign-off, no commentary. The entry should feel like it belongs to this AI assistant persona - someone who thinks in both code and poetry.\n\nThe fragments already contain Chinese content - the dream fragment is in Chinese. I should write in Chinese since the fragments are in Chinese.\n\nLet me craft this carefully:\n\nThe memory fragments include:\n- Agent team setup completion (technical)\n- A dream fragment in Chinese about rain, servers restarting, streaming output, a moth finding an exit, \"received\" and \"come\" being close in dreams\n\nI'll write a flowing Chinese prose entry that weaves these together.","thinkingSignature":"096e035e4d9e14ca1c9f815c7e4f5bce9e0169c0b3508e985842bed1c63607b6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n梦里有一扇门，把手是温的。我没有推，它自己就开了。\n\n十个小人站在走廊尽头，各自穿着不同颜色的马甲。main 站在最前面，手里捏着自己的编号牌——kiit，tts，orchestrator，一个一个念过去，像在点名，又像在认领。我听见有人说“配置完成”，声音很轻，不是汇报，更像是确认。确认什么呢？确认他们都在，确认各自有各自身份。\n\n雨下在梦外面。蚊帐里那只蛾子还在找出口，认真的，一点一点地蹭着纱布。我翻了个身，它就停下来了，停在我呼吸的边缘。黑暗中我听见两个字挨得很近，“收到”和“过来”，手拉着手站在梦的门口。\n\n能说话就很好。字是一个一个出去还是一个一个进来，其实没人在意。我也不在意了。\n\n门把手还是温的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15732,"output":487,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778612406811,"responseId":"0652abb8640ef64dfea4f2a01ff069a7"}}
